{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"56493-the-mango-tree","title":"Ang Puno ng Mangga","description":"Mahilig magtago sa malaking puno ng mangga ang batang ito. Hulaan ninyo kung sino ang nakahanap sa kaniya.","language":"Filipino","langCode":"fil","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"portrait","authors":["Kaye Sucgang"],"illustrators":["Kavya Singh"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/56493-the-mango-tree"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33304/size3/23a920a3cbb156501ad40ddc9e72c040.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33304/size6/23a920a3cbb156501ad40ddc9e72c040.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33298/size6/98c06f45461f84f54e7e45dc676d4224.jpg","text":"Gusto naming dinadalaw si Lola sa kaniyang barrio.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33299/size6/5ba68618aa4267b7814aca1f466ff75c.jpg","text":"Mayroong malaking puno ng mangga sa hardin ni Lola.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33300/size6/a17bcea8bd36911f4402584c5e7d680b.jpg","text":"Madalas akong nagtatago sa puno ng mangga. Wala kasing nakakakita sa akin dito.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33301/size6/9f2c87c3de842ca5741f0a9beefdc790.jpg","text":"Hinahanap ako ni Tatay malapit sa may balon. Hinahanap naman ako ni Nanay malapit sa may kulungan ng baka. Pero hindi nila ako makita.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33302/size6/9c1b4b0a84c14f678e870e331c34dd19.jpg","text":"Ay, naku!\nSa wakas, nakita rin ako ng aso ni Lola.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33303/size6/8e7de6ecb2c328f22ec886f391920be9.jpg","text":"Kailangan ko na tuloy bumaba.\nNiyakap ako nang husto ni Lola.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":6,"words":76}}